{"tid":2033741,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"BNO平權後 出黎打班細路繼續打 繼續坐監","createTime":"2020-05-24T23:55:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T18:09:12.000Z","uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"81eceb81b4867eecb1648b640d67f8f49229e7e5","tid":2033741,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T23:55:26.000Z","msg":"連天琦都走唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"901884595c38078a9da33e7c1b6291ba2adfd738","tid":2033741,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T00:01:09.000Z","msg":"雙非嗰班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceca4eee713eca6a38d6428a2eafb4c65b809130","tid":2033741,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T01:13:15.000Z","msg":"有得走唔走果啲<br />\n真香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c48da8a6ad717b6d396cfd2cb5482916232deb62","tid":2033741,"uid":304769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:07:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">BNO平權正視聽</span></span><br />\n連登一向有大量風向L、放負L，睇到BNO平權消息就用<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>割97後等風向挑撥離間</strong></span>，大家上連登請帶埋個腦。<br />\n<br />\n我從六月開始打英國戰線，希望嚮呢度講幾句。<br />\n第一，BNO平權唔會割97後，因為我地一向都係爭取救<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">BNO及其後代</span></strong>。，除非你係雙非，否則幾乎一定會受惠。<br />\n第二，BNO平權絕對係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>同美國行動有關係</strong></span>，故此毫無疑問就係一個救手足之舉，甚至可能與<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">軍事撤僑</span></strong>有關。<br />\n第三，BNO平到權主要唔係用包機包船黎接香港人去英國，亦都冇咩可能會接，畢竟人數太多。平到權最大重點係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>BNO變正式英國國民，中共逼害英國國民嘅話，英國以至美國就有理由做野</strong></span>。<br />\n第四，BNO平權估計會<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">寬鬆處理，英屬香港人（BOTC、BDTC、CUKC）無BNO或者已經過期應該都ok</span></strong>。因為英國情報已經判斷香港情況差到似烏干達難民。<br />\n第五，BNO平權大家可以更加無後顧之憂，因為將來要良民證黎移民，可以向英國當局申請。"},{"pid":"32ec277025205a930dafcd97f208cde7e3a91c09","tid":2033741,"uid":358640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T10:07:05.000Z","msg":"BNO平權有助香港建立海外屬地 黃色經濟圈全球化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2034495\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2034495</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bcd1fd8738c38d8d74271be5e508033f5b584299","tid":2033741,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T17:32:28.000Z","msg":"打手每日po抗爭相迫人出去繼續冇意義咁犧牲🤤🥴"},{"pid":"fd9c281630c3a0873df3aec6bc9dce447ee9883d","tid":2033741,"uid":39239,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T17:34:58.000Z","msg":"屌你啦 出篇新聞吹到實牙實齒<br />\n你哋班熱狗雲教共諜死全家"},{"pid":"e9d145a2831cc1cfca75f9f3873ec012c1ce6de1","tid":2033741,"uid":131282,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fd9c281630c3a0873df3aec6bc9dce447ee9883d","tid":2033741,"uid":39239,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T17:34:58.000Z","msg":"屌你啦 出篇新聞吹到實牙實齒<br />\n你哋班熱狗雲教共諜死全家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T18:09:12.000Z","msg":"有病😂就黎你踩個舊屎都係熱狗屙😂"}]}